Package: marcher
Type: Package
Title: Migration and Range-CHange Estimation in R
Version: 0.1
Date: 2016-12-27
Author: Eliezer Gurarie
Maintainer: Eliezer Gurarie <egurarie@umd.edu>
Description: Tools for likelihood estimation and model selection for various two- and three-range shift models for animal movement data. The method is described in detail in: E.Gurarie, F. Cagnacci, C. Fleming, W. Peters, J.M. Calabrese, T. MÃ¼ller and W. Fagan.  Whether, whither, when, and will it return?  A framework for modeling animal range shifts and migrations (in press) Journal of Animal Ecology. (It's pronounced "marshay!")
